features-properties-title: SUPPORT FOR MYANMAR'S REFORMS FOR INCLUSIVE GROWTH PROGRAM
features-properties-info: The policy-based loan will support Myanmar's re-engagement with global markets through key reform priorities aimed at generating broad-based, sustainable and inclusive economic growth
